{"tid":2380790,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金世正公開刺青！獨特圖案暗藏深意","createTime":"2021-01-26T06:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T12:01:01.000Z","uid":16659,"like":32,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e9a3bbe59ec8d9f863892108013717fa543078","tid":2380790,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T06:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_0b4c2cbf5b28db0149799e2b83a9bbbb/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-26/133278-894860.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_0b4c2cbf5b28db0149799e2b83a9bbbb%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-26%2F133278-894860.png&h=ae745d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金世正在主演電視劇而大獲好評的同時，所屬團體卻宣告解散⋯⋯短時間內經歷許多事情的她，最近便公開了別具意義的刺青！<br />\n<br />\n金世正昨天（25 日）在自己的 Instagram 上發出限時動態，拍下自己腳跟外側的一隻小烏龜刺青，並寫道：「哈囉」、「慢慢地長久走下去吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_4499f9576d4bc7514baf570a5c0ed864/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-26/133278-894861.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_4499f9576d4bc7514baf570a5c0ed864%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-26%2F133278-894861.png&h=395e42a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n偶像身上的刺青在近年來益發普遍，有別於通常刺下文字、迷你圖案的風格，金世正選擇形象鮮明但不常被刺上身的烏龜，似乎暗示著對未來事業的期許。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，金世正主演的 OCN 電視劇《驅魔麵館》最近完結，最後一集在全國和首都圈的收視率都飆破 10%，寫下開播以來的最佳成績！"},{"pid":"eade09342294c6bb7ff61f6f129986ded215bb81","tid":2380790,"uid":205928,"like":58,"dislike":9,"score":49,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T06:45:24.000Z","msg":"想奶佢隻腳再比我隻龜佢奶&hellip;"},{"pid":"1a79a64ad0ec2fea03b0e0c73ab19ef25c60d49c","tid":2380790,"uid":93096,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"eade09342294c6bb7ff61f6f129986ded215bb81","tid":2380790,"uid":205928,"like":58,"dislike":9,"score":49,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T06:45:24.000Z","msg":"想奶佢隻腳再比我隻龜佢奶&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T06:45:55.000Z","msg":"死細蚊仔色狗..."},{"pid":"a6de244010852a03f9c954184cde7f7